In short mcps are

| Concept         | Explanation                                         |
| --------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| **Full Name**   | Model Context Protocol                              |
| **Purpose**     | Standardizes how AI models talk to external systems |
| **Who Uses It** | ChatGPT, Claude, AI agents, automation frameworks   |
| **Key Benefit** | Secure, consistent, extensible tool integration     |
| **Similar To**  | API standard for LLMs (like REST for the web)       |
